'''''In Search Of Voodoo: Roots To Heaven''''' ni film ya documentaire ya biografiya yo muri [[Bene|Bénine]] 2018 iyobowe numukinnyi wamamaye wa Hollywood uzwi cyane Djimon Hounsou kandi afatanije numuyobozi ubwe hamwe na Eric McGaw<ref>https://www.imdb.com/name/nm5045249/</ref>.<ref>https://tubitv.com/movies/534760/in-search-of-voodoo-roots-to-heaven</ref><ref>https://bampfa.org/event/search-voodoo-roots-heaven</ref> 

Iyi filime ishingiye ku bintu byabayeho mu buzima bwumukinnyi Djimon Hounsou kandi yibanda ku nkuru z’umuntu ku giti cye, umuco, ndetse n’umwuka za Voodoo, muri [[Afurika]] y’iburengerazuba.  Filime yakiriwe neza nabayireba<ref>http://www.spla.pro/fiche.film.in-search-of-voodoo-roots-to-heaven.18277.html</ref><ref>https://variety.com/2018/film/reviews/in-search-of-voodoo-roots-to-heaven-review-1202723674/</ref>.<ref>https://mubi.com/films/in-search-of-voodoo-roots-to-heaven</ref> 

